{"tid":1672288,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[重要] 求解答 - 區議會選舉經費申報問題","createTime":"2019-10-24T04:21:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T12:26:27.000Z","uid":196197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"588c85737c1938afe7c84721806a11af283e497a","tid":1672288,"uid":196197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:21:41.000Z","msg":"假設一個選區有2位候選人：A 及 B，而我並不認識A或B，亦不是其助選團成員/義工。<br />\n<br />\nQ1: 如果我自費幫A印宣傳單張並於選區張貼，A是否要申報？A是否要將印宣傳單及張貼的費用計算入其競選經費內？如果A不能聯絡我，點知我印咗幾多宣傳單張？費用是多少？<br />\n<br />\nQ2: 如果我自費幫B印宣傳單張並於選區張貼，<span style=\"color: red;\">但內容是列出B過往的惡行並呼諭市民不要投票給B</span>，但沒有鼓勵投票給任何人，A是否有責任申報？還是責任在B？如該選區有3位或以上候選人又如何決定費用應該由邊位候選人承擔？<br />\n<br />\n跟據「區議會選舉資助計劃候選人須知」 <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/2019dcbe_2019ytmd_tn/2019dcbe_FAS_Notes_for_DCE_Candidates(Chi).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2F2019dcbe_2019ytmd_tn%2F2019dcbe_FAS_Notes_for_DCE_Candidates%28Chi%29.pdf&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUocyzqlNZT0%2FxJNtMGMfIkD0%3D&h=167a609c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/2019dcbe_2019ytmd_tn/2019dcbe_FAS_Notes_for_DCE_Candidates(Chi).pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n7(b) ：曾由該候選人或由他人代該候選人在與該項選舉有關連的情況下收取的所有選舉捐贈均需申報。<br />\nQ1情況是否屬於「由他人代該候選人」捐贈？<br />\n<br />\n第12條：任何組織或個人給予候選人用以支付或有助於支付其選舉開支的任何財政利益，均應申報為選舉捐贈，並記帳於選舉申報書內。任何免費或以折扣價獲取的貨品及服務，均屬實物抵付形式的選舉捐贈，其估計合理價值應納入選舉申報書，同時列為選舉捐贈及選舉開支 （ 如適用 ） 。由政治團體或任何組織舉辦的籌款活動，如沒有特別提及候選人，則不被計算為候選人的選舉活動。不過，該等政治團體或組織以是次選舉為目的而給予候選人的任何捐獻，均須記錄為候選人收取的選舉捐贈。<br />\nQ2情況會否適用於12條？<br />\n<br />\n請法律JJ幫手解答。因為我覺得好多候選人我哋都可以用 Q2 方法幫佢助選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cfaf59cea573fedd2b1d3a581da0c7799c40a98","tid":1672288,"uid":196197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:25:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94f562e0dfd90bc304e8cd40de30aafb75ea2962","tid":1672288,"uid":196197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:26:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8572a2efb5a7908a1082b5f87bb887470b876591","tid":1672288,"uid":196197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:31:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9448ae30302682c8becaf6a60b048ef6cf8bac9e","tid":1672288,"uid":196197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d95fa126d5818034fa33f187189d8a84b22edd","tid":1672288,"uid":253758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:47:50.000Z","msg":"Q1：您會搞到A被人查，另如果A到時唔認數，話宣傳品唔係佢做，您會有刑責。<br />\n<br />\nQ2：一樣，被人捉到，您會有刑責。<br />\n<br />\n利申：幫人助選過。"},{"pid":"47c8f68af0e978a7f82069ef8fe0df4d22330a44","tid":1672288,"uid":196197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9d95fa126d5818034fa33f187189d8a84b22edd","tid":1672288,"uid":253758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:47:50.000Z","msg":"Q1：您會搞到A被人查，另如果A到時唔認數，話宣傳品唔係佢做，您會有刑責。<br />\n<br />\nQ2：一樣，被人捉到，您會有刑責。<br />\n<br />\n利申：幫人助選過。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T05:53:37.000Z","msg":"刑責前題係俾人捉到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nQ2 就算俾人捉到，都唔關A事？"},{"pid":"0ff78517e68b097fbfedd4c34f03d4aedb7c31b3","tid":1672288,"uid":319235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T12:26:27.000Z","msg":"[和理Post] 過嚟問下啲區議員候選人喇喂<br />\n傳送門：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/4c2gWbS1B715fFDu6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F4c2gWbS1B715fFDu6&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUocyzqlNZT0%2FxJNtMGMfIkD0%3D&h=903270dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/4c2gWbS1B715fFDu6</a><br />\n<br />\n連登Post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1666510\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1666510</a>"}]}